Package Graph

Class Graph

java.lang.Object
Graph.Graph
public class Graph extends Object
The Graph class represents a graph and its properties. It contains an array of Vertex objects, an adjacency matrix, the number of vertices and edges, the chromatic number, and the upper and lower bounds of the graph.
